  • Rated 5 out of 5 stars

    Excellent Starter for Push Button Cars

    Very Cool remote starter, also has super long range remote. It's amazing how far i can start my car, 2-way confirmation is a plus. This Starter paired with my push button Start Acura TLX Aspec allows for take over mode, which is a plus. I also got Drone mobile with this Starter for unlimited range. Factory key-Fob also can now start my car. Geek Squad Installer was very professional and knowledgeable about the products installed in my vehicle. Installation took a little longer than expected, but the wait was worth it. Winter time is now comfortable with remote start. All cars should have remote start feature.
